data.title: China’s robotics twin stars join national committee to shape industry standards
data.description: Unitree’s Wang Xingxing and AgiBot’s Peng Zhihui have been appointed to the Standardisation Technical Committee for Humanoid Robots.
data.keywords: Beijing, Unitree Robotics, Peng Zhihui, Tsinghua University, Xpeng, Huawei Technologies, AgiBot, MIIT, Shanghai Stock Exchange, China, US, Leju Robotics, Baidu, Wang Xingxing, Shenzhen-based UBTech Robotics
